narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Complete Transit is a Non-emergency Medical Transport (VAN) provider based in Milwaukee, WI. From 2024-04 through 2024-12, this provider received $176K in Medicaid payments across 3K claims serving 588 beneficiaries, billing 1 distinct procedure codes.

narrative.title: Key Findings
items: Bills 2.9× the national median for T2003 (T2003), at $63 per claim vs. the median of $22, placing them above the 75th percentile.
100% of billing is concentrated in T2003 (T2003), indicating significant specialization in this service.
